<p>
This is a long text and we intend to show only this much unless the user presses the show more button below.
</p>

{{#if showMoreText}}
  <p>
    This is the reamining text that should be visible when we press the show more button. Ideally this should contain a lot more text, but for example's sake this should be enough
  </p>
  <br/><br/>
  <button {{action 'toggleMore'}}>Toggle Less</button>
{{else}}
  <button {{action 'toggleMore'}}>Show More</button>
{{/if}}
